Name: Average time from SW-Reviewer Agreed to SW-EIC Reject
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'SW-Reviewer Agreed' and activity 'SW-EIC Reject'

Name: Total time between SW-Awaiting EIC Decision and SW-EIC Reject
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'SW-Awaiting EIC Decision' and activity 'SW-EIC Reject'

Name: Minimum time it takes SW-EIC Reject to be performed after SW-Reviewer Agreed
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'SW-Reviewer Agreed' and activity 'SW-EIC Reject'

Name: Average time for SW-EIC Reject across all variants where it appears as a terminal activity
Metric: The average of the duration between activity SW-EIC Reject and the end of the case

Name: Total resolution time of SW-EIC Reject in cases that included at least one reviewer agreement (SW-Reviewer Agreed)
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'SW-EIC Reject' and the end of case where activity 'SW-Reviewer Agreed occurs

Name: Time elapsed between the last occurrence of SW-Reviewer Agreed and SW-EIC Reject within the same case
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'SW-Reviewer Agreed' and activity 'SW-EIC Reject'

Name: Average time from SW-AE Recommendation overdue to SW-EIC Reject
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'SW-AE Recommendation overdue' and activity 'SW-EIC Reject'

Name: Minimum time between SW-Awaiting EIC Decision and SW-EIC Reject in variants with high reviewer turnover (e.g., multiple SW-Reviewer Declined or SW-Reviewer No Response)
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'SW-Awaiting EIC Decision' and activity 'SW-EIC Reject'

Name: Total time it takes SW-EIC Reject to occur after the first submission-related activity (Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation)
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation' and activity 'SW-EIC Reject'

Name: Time from SW-Checklist Completed to SW-EIC Reject in rejected manuscripts that never entered revision phases
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'SW-Checklist Completed' and activity 'SW-EIC Reject'

Name: Total time between Manuscript Export Succeeded and SW-EIC Reject in direct-rejection variants (without intermediate reviewer activities)
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Manuscript Export Succeeded' and activity 'SW-EIC Reject'

Name: Average time it takes SW-EIC Reject to be executed after the final reviewer response (last occurrence of SW-Reviewer Agreed, SW-Reviewer Declined, or SW-Reviewer No Response)
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'SW-Reviewer Agreed' and activity 'SW-EIC Reject'

Name: Time elapsed from SW-AE Assign Reviewers to SW-EIC Reject in cases where no reviewer ever agreed (absence of SW-Reviewer Agreed)
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'SW-AE Assign Reviewers' and activity 'SW-EIC Reject'

Name: Average cycle time of SW-EIC Reject when preceded by SW–Major Revision due in 1 week versus SW–Minor Revision due in 1 week
Metric: The average of the duration between activity SW-EIC Reject and the end of the case
